{title: Windows Line Endings}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]This file uses [C]CRLF line [D]endings
[G]Like files from [C]Windows [D]machines
[Em]Carriage return [C]before each [D]newline
[G]In all of these [C]lines and [D]scenes
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Windows [G]style
[D]Line [Em]breaks
[C]Backslash [G]r
[D]Backslash [G]n
{end_of_chorus}
